	  	<p>Ecore is the metamodel used by EMF to define other metamodels. The Ecore graphical editor is a part of the TOPCASED-MF (for Modeling Framework) subproject.</p>

	    <p>
	    	If you are interested in <b>developing and contributing</b> enhancements or new capabilities for the Ecore editor, please go to the <xref format="html" href="http://gforge.enseeiht.fr/projects/topcased-mf/" scope="external">
	    	developers area </xref> , you will find all necessary informations. Any contribution is welcome !
	    </p>
	
	    <p>If you find a <b>bug</b> , or if you are thinking to an <b>improvement</b> of the toolset, please fill a <xref format="html" href="http://gforge.enseeiht.fr/tracker/?group_id=7" scope="external">bug/feature request report</xref>.</p>

